{"tid":989990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一日第二宗】大埔富善邨鋁窗飛墜　警刑事調查隊跟進","createTime":"2019-01-21T09:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T09:29:28.000Z","uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f98ef9569eab9c4f1029a5f68b4a5c9a4f50a10","tid":989990,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"一日內發生兩宗高空墜窗事件。下午12時許，大埔富善邨善美樓一扇鋁窗從高處墜下，跌至大廈對開樹底石壆，幸無撃中途人。該鋁窗大小約半米乘一米，玻璃碎裂窗框變形，由保安架設欄杆圍封及報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場調查，案件列容許物件從高處墜下，交大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n今早10時許，尖沙嘴美麗華酒店一扇鋁窗疑因鬆脫從16樓飛墜，一名女途人被擊中頭部陷入昏迷，送院搶救不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190121/s00001/1548059246276/%e3%80%90%e4%b8%80%e6%97%a5%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e5%ae%97%e3%80%91%e5%a4%a7%e5%9f%94%e5%af%8c%e5%96%84%e9%82%a8%e9%8b%81%e7%aa%97%e9%a3%9b%e5%a2%9c-%e8%ad%a6%e5%88%91%e4%ba%8b%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5%e9%9a%8a%e8%b7%9f%e9%80%b2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190121%2Fs00001%2F1548059246276%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2597%25a5%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e5%25ae%2597%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259f%2594%25e5%25af%258c%25e5%2596%2584%25e9%2582%25a8%25e9%258b%2581%25e7%25aa%2597%25e9%25a3%259b%25e5%25a2%259c-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2588%2591%25e4%25ba%258b%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5%25e9%259a%258a%25e8%25b7%259f%25e9%2580%25b2&d=w7%2FbDBVMSsXhjs7ptAmemC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a6910a95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190121%2Fs00001%2F1548059246276%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2597%25a5%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e5%25ae%2597%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259f%2594%25e5%25af%258c%25e5%2596%2584%25e9%2582%25a8%25e9%258b%2581%25e7%25aa%2597%25e9%25a3%259b%25e5%25a2%259c-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2588%2591%25e4%25ba%258b%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5%25e9%259a%258a%25e8